## Common Mistakes

### Mistake 1: Hook File with Hidden Component
```typescript
// File: useLogic.ts ❌
export const useLogic = () => {
  // Hidden component at the bottom!
  const Icon = () => <Icon.Tick />; // JSX present!

  return { Icon };
};

// Should be: useLogic.tsx ✅
```

## Code Review Checklist

- [ ] All component files are `.tsx` (or `.jsx`)
- [ ] All files with JSX are `.tsx` (or `.jsx`)
- [ ] Hook files with components are `.tsx`
- [ ] Utility files without JSX are `.ts`
- [ ] Type definition files are `.ts` (never `.tsx`)
- [ ] Constant files are `.ts`

